  "title": "Magnetism - identifying polarity with known magnet",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a horizontal bar with its left end labeled A and its right end labeled B.\" src=\"/images/bd6dd7228c01def6322b46f6891121c0.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A student is given a metal bar with ends labeled <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi></math></span></span>. The student suspects that the bar may be a magnet and wants to determine which end of the bar is magnetic north. The student brings end <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> near the north end of a bar magnet and observes that the two ends attract. Which of the following best describes the polarity of end <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> before the student brought it near the bar magnet?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i3",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">End <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> <span class=\"formatted_text text_decoration:underline\">must</span> be magnetic north.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">End <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> <span class=\"formatted_text text_decoration:underline\">must</span> be magnetic south.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">End <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> <span class=\"formatted_text text_decoration:underline\">may</span> be magnetic south.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It is impossible to determine if end <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi></math></span></span> is magnetic north or south with this information.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      }
    ]
